        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1488436967" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10462669688428046482">St. Therese of Lisieux is one of the most beloved Catholic saints. So what is her story? And why are so many devoted to her?<br/><br/>St. Therese was born to parents who deeply loved the church. Their children were raised in that atmosphere, so it is no surprise that several became nuns, including Therese. <br/><br/>Therese wrote down the story of her life in this little book. In it, the reader gets a feel for the astonishing character that was Therese. She seemed to live her faith every minute of the day. Simply. </span>
  <span id="freeText10462669688428046482" style="display:none">St. Therese of Lisieux is one of the most beloved Catholic saints. So what is her story? And why are so many devoted to her?<br /><br />St. Therese was born to parents who deeply loved the church. Their children were raised in that atmosphere, so it is no surprise that several became nuns, including Therese. <br /><br />Therese wrote down the story of her life in this little book. In it, the reader gets a feel for the astonishing character that was Therese. She seemed to live her faith every minute of the day. Simply. Devoutly. She was completely devoted to God.<br /><br />Beautiful and inspiring story.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10462669688428046482" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

