<div id="review_2757379077" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2757379077" />
    <a title="Lawrence Jakows" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/93829798-lawrence-jakows"><img alt="Lawrence Jakows" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1552437100p2/93829798.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2757379077?book_show_action=true">Mar 20, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lawrence Jakows" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lawrence Jakows" href="/user/show/93829798-lawrence-jakows">Lawrence Jakows</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/18592295-the-story-of-a-soul-l-histoire-d-une-me">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/93829798-lawrence-jakows?shelf=saints">saints</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2757379077" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4815913441247841714">A wonderful story from a beautiful saint. She is quoted several times in my book &quot;Jesus: Perfect Love.&quot; During her time at the Carmel, she discovers her vocation is: love! Her Little Way, her sacrifices, her devotion to His Holy Face, her complete love of her Lord are just a few of the reasons why this book has been popular for over one hundred years.</span>
  <span id="freeText4815913441247841714" style="display:none">A wonderful story from a beautiful saint. She is quoted several times in my book "Jesus: Perfect Love." During her time at the Carmel, she discovers her vocation is: love! Her Little Way, her sacrifices, her devotion to His Holy Face, her complete love of her Lord are just a few of the reasons why this book has been popular for over one hundred years.</span>
  <a data-text-id="4815913441247841714" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


