<div id="review_3970081627" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3970081627" />
    <a title="Meghan Furey" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/25057887-meghan-furey"><img alt="Meghan Furey" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1382727428p2/25057887.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3970081627?book_show_action=true">Apr 30, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Meghan Furey" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Meghan Furey" href="/user/show/25057887-meghan-furey">Meghan Furey</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3970081627" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6969974893748235772">Ugh how I WISH St. Therese was alive still today! Reading this made me feel like I was listening to the words of a soul sister or friend in Christ. <br/><br/>Besides her journey of faith, I loved reading about her family and her relationship with her father. He used to call her his little queen. Reminds me of my poppy hehe<br/><br/>But this book is so raw with beautiful thoughts and words of a saint that has had a major impact on my life and I am so glad to have finally read it!! <br/><br/>The key to life is LOVE and perform</span>
  <span id="freeText6969974893748235772" style="display:none">Ugh how I WISH St. Therese was alive still today! Reading this made me feel like I was listening to the words of a soul sister or friend in Christ. <br /><br />Besides her journey of faith, I loved reading about her family and her relationship with her father. He used to call her his little queen. Reminds me of my poppy hehe<br /><br />But this book is so raw with beautiful thoughts and words of a saint that has had a major impact on my life and I am so glad to have finally read it!! <br /><br />The key to life is LOVE and performing little acts of love for others 🤗 </span>
